msContents.summary: Student notes, examples, and exercises for algebra, trigonometry, and geometry.

supportDesc.extent: 88 leaves : 205 x 165 mm. bound to 209 x 175 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Paper, 88; 1-24, [i], 25-30, 40-65, 70-86, 89-164, 167, [xxiii], contemporary pagination in ink, upper outer corners; [1-88], modern foliation in pencil, upper right recto. References in this record are to modern foliation.

layoutDesc.layout: Text passages written in 18-20 lines per page, ruled in lead.

decoDesc.decoNote: Decorated table of contents (f. 1v) and section headings; numerous geometrical diagrams and drawings.

binding.p: 18th-century quarter leather, with much of the leather on the covers now gone.
